# 🧠 3. REST BASICS = Menu-Based Ordering System

## 🔹 Sub-skills

* HTTP methods (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
* Endpoints
* Status codes
* Idempotency

---

## 🔹 WH (Core)

* **What** → Standard way to build APIs
* **Why** → Simple, scalable communication
