### HTTP Methods

* What → Action types
* Why → Define operation
* How → GET/POST etc.
  👉 Analogy: Order type (view/order/update)

### Endpoints

* What → API URLs
* Why → Access resources
* How → Structured routes
  👉 Analogy: Menu items

### Status Codes

* What → Response signals
* Why → Inform result
* How → 200, 404, 500
